You got the syntax slightly wrong:

```java
declare @field :
  (@javax.persistence.OneToOne *) foo.bar.MyEntity : 
  @org.hibernate.annotations.Cache(usage = org.hibernate.annotations.CacheConcurrencyStrategy.READ_ONLY);
